%% Pattern A: Turn Signal Sequence - v2
%% Key change from v1: LLM no longer polls. kernel.wait_for_event blocks in Python.
%% LLM invokes one tool call and is unblocked when event fires (Gemini recommendation).
%% Validated E2: 2.17s full round-trip, 28x faster than file-flip protocol.

sequenceDiagram
  autonumber

  participant ORC as ORCHESTRATOR
  participant K as kernel.py
  participant BUS as events.jsonl
  participant INBOX as PEER inbox.jsonl
  participant PEER as PEER_AGENT
  participant MEM as memory.md

  Note over ORC,MEM: Session start - register on project-scoped bus

  ORC->>K: emit agent.registered with heartbeat schedule
  K->>BUS: append + validate against agents.json
  PEER->>K: emit agent.registered with heartbeat schedule
  K->>BUS: append + validate

  Note over ORC,MEM: Heartbeats run every 30s in background - PEER monitors ORCHESTRATOR

  ORC->>K: apply fix to skill, emit fix.applied with correlation_id
  K->>BUS: append, spinlock acquired and released atomically

  ORC->>K: deliver_event to PEER - signal.wakeup, assignment: run eval
  K->>INBOX: atomic append to PEER inbox.jsonl
  Note over ORC: ORCHESTRATOR does NOT poll or wait in LLM context

  ORC->>K: wait_for_event --to ORCHESTRATOR --action eval.result --timeout 120
  Note over ORC: Python blocks internally - LLM context is free

  Note over PEER: PEER reads own inbox - no bus scanning
  PEER->>INBOX: read new entries since last cursor
  INBOX-->>PEER: signal.wakeup detected in inbox

  PEER->>PEER: sync skill from canonical store
  PEER->>PEER: run eval_runner against updated skill

  PEER->>K: emit eval.result - score and baseline - correlation_id matches
  K->>BUS: append
  K->>INBOX: deliver to ORCHESTRATOR inbox

  Note over ORC: kernel.wait_for_event unblocks - returns event to LLM
  K-->>ORC: eval.result received - Python unblocks

  alt score meets or exceeds baseline
    ORC->>ORC: confirm commit, push to origin
    ORC->>K: emit fix.confirmed with correlation_id
    K->>BUS: append
    ORC->>K: deliver_event to PEER - next assignment
    K->>INBOX: append to PEER inbox
  else score regression detected
    ORC->>ORC: investigate diff, apply correction
    ORC->>K: emit fix.applied v2 - regression corrected
    K->>BUS: append
    ORC->>K: deliver_event to PEER - re-eval same skill
    K->>INBOX: append to PEER inbox
  end

  Note over ORC,MEM: After N cycles - memory promotion with source citation
  PEER->>MEM: session-memory-manager promotes facts - each entry cites session source
  ORC->>MEM: write architecture decisions with citation
